Tuesday, June 30, 2020
Today, Texas reports 6,975 more confirmed cases of COVID-19.  A new single day record in Texas.
The previous 7 days:
Monday - 4,288
Sunday - 5,357
Saturday - 5,742
Friday - 5,707
Thursday - 5,996.
Wed. - 5,551
Tue. - 5,489
A total of 45,105 cases.
